# MCP Image Generator API Examples
# Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@prodUrl = https://your-agentcore-endpoint.amazonaws.com

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: application/json

### Detailed Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

### List MCP Tools
POST {{baseUrl}}/mcp/tools/list
Content-Type: application/json

### Generate Image - Basic (Stability AI)
POST {{baseUrl}}/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "A serene mountain landscape at sunset with snow-capped peaks and a crystal clear lake",
  "model": "stability",
  "width": 1024,
  "height": 1024
}

### Generate Image - Photographic Style
POST {{baseUrl}}/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "A professional portrait of a confident business woman in modern office",
  "model": "stability",
  "width": 1024,
  "height": 1024,
  "style": "photographic",
  "cfg_scale": 7.0,
  "steps": 50
}

### Generate Image - Digital Art Style
POST {{baseUrl}}/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "A majestic dragon flying over a fantasy castle with magical aurora in the sky",
  "model": "stability",
  "width": 1024,
  "height": 1024,
  "style": "digital-art",
  "cfg_scale": 8.0,
  "steps": 60
}

