### Error Test - Missing Prompt
POST {{baseUrl}}/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "stability"
}

### Error Test - Invalid Model
POST {{baseUrl}}/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "A test image",
  "model": "invalid_model"
}

### Error Test - Invalid Dimensions
POST {{baseUrl}}/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "A test image",
  "model": "stability",
  "width": 100,
  "height": 100
}
